* {{cite news|url=https://www.ciudad.com.ar/espectaculos/las-mejores-20-fotos-explosivo-show-ricky-martin-buenos-aires-sensualidad_131947|title=Las mejores 20 fotos del explosivo show de Ricky Martin en Buenos Aires: sensualidad, emoción y mucho baile|publisher=[[Ciudad Magazine]]|language=es|date=February 28, 2020|access-date=January 18, 2022}}</ref> ''Billboard''{{'}}s Marjua Estevez described Martin's performance of "La Copa de la Vida" at the 41st Annual Grammy Awards as "the most memorable Latin performance at a Grammy Awards show",<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/latin/past-latin-performances-at-the-grammys-8093731/|title=How Rare Is a Latin Performance at the Grammys? Very|last=Estevez|first=Marjua|magazine=Billboard|access-date=May 5, 2021|date=January 10, 2018}}</ref> and the publication ranked it as the 54th Greatest Award Show Performance of All Time on their 2017 list.<ref name="Billboard 54">{{Cite magazine|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/awards/best-award-show-performances-of-all-time-7677099/|title=The 100 Greatest Award Show Performances of All Time|magazine=Billboard|date=February 8, 2017|access-date=May 6, 2021}}</ref> The performance was additionally placed on a 2017 unranked list of "Top 20 Best Grammy Performances of All Time" by [[Gold Derby]],<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.goldderby.com/gallery/top-20-best-grammy-performances-of-all-time-photos/7-ricky-martin-la-copa-de-la-vida/|title=Top 20 Best Grammy Performances of All Time|publisher=Gold Derby|date=February 12, 2017|access-date=May 6, 2021}}</ref> and on a 2019 list of "The Most Unforgettable Grammys Performances of All Time" by ''[[InStyle]]''.<ref name="InStyle">{{Cite web|url=https://www.instyle.com/news/most-unforgettable-grammys-performances-all-time?slide=56042d58-bb5b-4e59-a45c-8f6b2ea85407#56042d58-bb5b-4e59-a45c-8f6b2ea85407|title=The Most Unforgettable Grammys Performances of All Time|work=[[InStyle]]|date=January 1, 2019|access-date=May 6, 2021}}</ref>

==Public image==
Martin became a [[teen idol]] with his debut as a member of Menudo,<ref name="Hola actor"/><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/lifestyle/style/1999/05/09/boys-to-men/2a3cc9cc-3681-4d2f-a9d4-408eb64dca41/|title=Boys to Men|newspaper=[[The Washington Post]]|last=Harrington|first=Richard|date=May 9, 1999|access-date=January 19, 2022|archive-date=January 19, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119192202/https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/lifestyle/style/1999/05/09/boys-to-men/2a3cc9cc-3681-4d2f-a9d4-408eb64dca41/|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="RS Nancy">{{cite magazine|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/ricky-martin-the-rolling-stone-interview-179825/|title=Ricky Martin: The Rolling Stone Interview|magazine=Rolling Stone|last=Collins|first=Nancy|date=August 5, 1999|access-date=January 19, 2022|archive-date=January 19, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119192216/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/ricky-martin-the-rolling-stone-interview-179825/|url-status=live}}</ref> and a [[pop icon]] following global fame as a solo artist.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.gaytimes.co.uk/culture/ricky-martin-teams-up-with-onepulse-foundation-for-new-outlove-hate-campaign/|title=Ricky Martin teams up with onePulse foundation for new Outlove Hate campaign|work=[[Gay Times]]|last=Robledo|first=Jordan|access-date=January 19, 2022|archive-date=January 19, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119192216/https://www.gaytimes.co.uk/culture/ricky-martin-teams-up-with-onepulse-foundation-for-new-outlove-hate-campaign/|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/news/latino/latin-grammys-have-hard-time-awarding-urban-music-even-after-n1081066|title=Latin Grammys have a hard time awarding urban music, even after 20 years|publisher=NBC News|last=Acevedo|first=Nicole|date=November 14, 2019|access-date=January 19, 2022|archive-date=January 19, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119192341/https://www.nbcnews.com/news/latino/latin-grammys-have-hard-time-awarding-urban-music-even-after-n1081066|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.huffpost.com/entry/lgbt-history-month-icon-ricky-martin_n_1937569|title=LGBT History Month Icon Of The Day: Ricky Martin|work=HuffPost|last=Tungol|first=JR|date=November 14, 2012|access-date=January 19, 2022|archive-date=January 19, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119192237/https://www.huffpost.com/entry/lgbt-history-month-icon-ricky-martin_n_1937569|url-status=live}}</ref> Journalists have written about his humble personality and "beautiful soul".<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.smh.com.au/entertainment/music/latino-superstar-ricky-martin-shakes-perths-bonbon-20131013-2vg1l.html|title=Latino superstar Ricky Martin shakes Perth's bon-bon|work=The Sydney Morning Herald|last=Nazzari|first=Natalie|date=October 13, 2013|access-date=January 19, 2022|archive-date=January 19, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119192340/https://www.smh.com.au/entertainment/music/latino-superstar-ricky-martin-shakes-perths-bonbon-20131013-2vg1l.html|url-status=live}}</ref> Writing for ''The Hollywood Reporter'', Scott Feinberg introduced Martin as "one of the most acclaimed and admired creative artists ever".<ref name="HRCup"/> ''[[La República]]'' staff described him as "one of the most admired and desired singers", while authors of ''[[¡Hola!]]'' described him as "one of the most respected Latin stars in the world", "one of the most prodigious voices in music in Spanish", and "one of the most beloved talents in the entertainment industry worldwide".<ref name="Hola actor"/><ref>{{cite news|url=https://larepublica.pe/espectaculos/2021/09/30/ricky-martin-cual-es-el-retoque-que-se-hizo-y-por-que-es-el-mas-solicitado-atmp/|title=Ricky Martin: ¿cuál es el retoque que se habría hecho la estrella puertorriqueña?|work=[[La República]]|language=es|date=September 30, 2021|access-date=January 19, 2022|archive-date=January 19, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119192339/https://larepublica.pe/espectaculos/2021/09/30/ricky-martin-cual-es-el-retoque-que-se-hizo-y-por-que-es-el-mas-solicitado-atmp/|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.hola.com/us-es/entretenimiento/20220127308972/ricky-martin-estreno-sencillo-video-otra-noche-en-la/|title=Ricky Martin está de estreno con su sencillo 'Otra Noche en L.A.'|language=es|work=¡Hola!|access-date=January 29, 2022|date=January 27, 2022|archive-date=January 29, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220129102706/https://www.hola.com/us-es/entretenimiento/20220127308972/ricky-martin-estreno-sencillo-video-otra-noche-en-la/|url-status=live}}</ref> Also from ''¡Hola!'', Cristina Noé named him "one of the most loved artists in the world",<ref name="Hola Hotel">{{cite news|url=https://www.hola.com/us/celebrities/20200227fl2721z0e6/ricky-martin-sweet-gesture-fans-argentina-hotel/|title=Ricky Martin's Hotel Is Under Siege With Fans - But His Reaction Was The Last Thing They Expected|work=¡Hola!|last=Noé|first=Cristina|date=February 27, 2020|access-date=January 19, 2022|archive-date=January 19, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119192404/https://www.hola.com/us/celebrities/20200227fl2721z0e6/ricky-martin-sweet-gesture-fans-argentina-hotel/|url-status=live}}</ref> while a writer of ''[[Clarín (Argentine newspaper)|Clarín]]'' named him "one of the most applauded Latin singers on the planet".<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.clarin.com/espectaculos/musica/explosiva-primera-noche-ricky-martin-buenos-aires-11-mil-personas_0_qvEFHfPu.html|title=La explosiva primera noche de Ricky Martin en Buenos Aires ante 11 mil personas|work=[[Clarín (Argentine newspaper)|Clarín]]|language=es|date=February 27, 2020|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120145916/https://www.clarin.com/espectaculos/musica/explosiva-primera-noche-ricky-martin-buenos-aires-11-mil-personas_0_qvEFHfPu.html|url-status=live}}</ref> ''[[Metro International|Metro Puerto Rico]]'' stated that he "raised the name of Puerto Rico internationally".<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.metro.pr/pr/entretenimiento/2021/12/24/fotogaleria-mira-luce-ricky-martin-50-anos.html|title=Fotogalería: Mira como luce Ricky Martin a sus 50 años|work=Metro Puerto Rico|language=es|date=December 24, 2021|access-date=February 2, 2022|archive-date=February 2, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220202124533/https://www.metro.pr/pr/entretenimiento/2021/12/24/fotogaleria-mira-luce-ricky-martin-50-anos.html|url-status=live}}</ref> He was ranked as one of the top-10 "emerging personalities" of 2010 by [[Google Trends|Google Zeitgeist]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.foxnews.com/entertainment/ricky-martin-channels-george-michael-on-new-album-cover|title=Ricky Martin Channels George Michael On New Album Cover|publisher=[[Fox News]]|last=Gratereaux|first=Alexandra J.|date=December 14, 2010|access-date=January 19, 2022|archive-date=January 19, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119193222/https://www.foxnews.com/entertainment/ricky-martin-channels-george-michael-on-new-album-cover|url-status=live}}</ref> In 2014, ''[[Gay Star News]]'' referred to Martin as "the most famous Latin pop star in the world", while ''Variety'' described him as "Puerto Rico's arguably most famous son" in 2021.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.gaystarnews.com/article/are-ricky-martin-and-ian-thorpe-now-couple120914/|title=Are Ricky Martin and Ian Thorpe now a couple?|work=[[Gay Star News]]|last=Smith|first=Tris Reid|date=September 12, 2014|access-date=January 19, 2022|archive-date=January 19, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119192428/https://www.gaystarnews.com/article/are-ricky-martin-and-ian-thorpe-now-couple120914/|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2021/film/news/sundance-el-cuartito-1234896237/|title=Particular Crowd Grabs Rights to Marcos Carnevale's Dramedy 'El Cuartito' (Exclusive)|work=Variety|last=Marie de la Fuente|first=Anna|date=January 30, 2021|access-date=January 19, 2022|archive-date=January 19, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119192438/https://variety.com/2021/film/news/sundance-el-cuartito-1234896237/|url-status=live}}</ref> He is ranked as the second-most famous Latin music artist in the United States, according to [[YouGov]] surveys in 2021.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://today.yougov.com/ratings/entertainment/fame/latin-music-artists/all|title=The Most Famous Latin Music Artists|publisher=[[YouGov]]|access-date=January 19, 2022|archive-date=January 19, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119192650/https://today.yougov.com/ratings/entertainment/fame/latin-music-artists/all|url-status=dead}}</ref>

During the 2000s, Martin was known for "guarding his private life" and being "uncomfortable discussing intimate aspects of his personal life"; he used to insist on asking public to focus on his music and "steered interviewers away from his personal life".<ref>{{cite news|title=Ready to live the family life?|url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/92966971/the-sacramento-bee/|newspaper=[[The Sacramento Bee]]|date=June 23, 2003|page=A2|via=Newspapers.com|access-date=January 19, 2022|archive-date=January 19, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119192545/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/92966971/the-sacramento-bee/|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Ricky Martin's new CD offers more upbeat tunes|url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/92969495/courier-post/|newspaper=Courier-Post|date=November 16, 2000|page=37|via=Newspapers.com|access-date=January 19, 2022|archive-date=January 19, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119192530/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/92969495/courier-post/|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="E! influential">{{cite news|url=https://www.eonline.com/news/1305270/how-ricky-martin-became-one-of-the-most-influential-latinx-and-lgtbq-artists-in-the-world|title=How Ricky Martin Became One of the Most Influential Artists in the World|work=[[E! Online]]|last=Finn|first=Natalie|date=December 25, 2021|access-date=January 19, 2022|archive-date=January 19, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119192654/https://www.eonline.com/news/1305270/how-ricky-martin-became-one-of-the-most-influential-latinx-and-lgtbq-artists-in-the-world|url-status=live}}</ref> However, he chose to live both his "professional and personal life", making his private life public since the early 2010s.<ref name="Variety Come out"/><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.jpost.com/israel-news/culture/lovin-la-vida-loca-with-ricky-martin-466586|title=Lovin' la vida loca with Ricky Martin|last=Keenan|first=Katherine|work=The Jerusalem Post|access-date=September 3, 2021|date=September 1, 2016|archive-date=September 3, 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210903140407/https://www.jpost.com/israel-news/culture/lovin-la-vida-loca-with-ricky-martin-466586|url-status=live}}</ref> In 2021, he went on the cover of ''People'' with the title "No More Secrets" and told the magazine that he is "a man with no secrets", stating that he is "more comfortable in his own skin than ever before".<ref name="People No Secrets">{{cite news| url=https://people.com/music/ricky-martin-wont-hide-anymore-man-with-no-secrets-pride-cover/| title=Ricky Martin Doesn't Want to Hide Who He Is Anymore: 'I Am a Man with No Secrets'|last=Sheeler|first=Jason|work=People|access-date=June 9, 2021|date=June 2, 2021|archive-date=June 9, 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210609101753/https://people.com/music/ricky-martin-wont-hide-anymore-man-with-no-secrets-pride-cover/|url-status=live}}</ref> Martin is one of the most followed celebrities on social media,<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.enpareja.com/break/Valentino-Martin-el-hijo-de-13-anos-de-Ricky-Martin-rey-del-Tik-Tok-20220103-0032.html|title=Valentino Martin el hijo de 13 años de Ricky Martin rey del Tik Tok|work=En Pareja|language=es|last=Chavez|first=Nadxiely|date=January 3, 2022|access-date=January 19, 2022|archive-date=January 19, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119192704/https://www.enpareja.com/break/Valentino-Martin-el-hijo-de-13-anos-de-Ricky-Martin-rey-del-Tik-Tok-20220103-0032.html|url-status=live}}</ref> with accounts on [[Instagram]],<ref>{{Cite news|title=Ricky Martin (@ricky_martin) • Instagram photos and videos|url=https://www.instagram.com/ricky_martin/|publisher=[[Instagram]]|access-date=January 19, 2022|url-status=live}}</ref> [[Twitter]],<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://twitter.com/ricky_martin|title=Ricky Martin (@ricky_martin) · Twitter|publisher=[[Twitter]]|access-date=January 19, 2022|archive-date=January 19, 2022|archive-url=|url-status=live}}</ref> [[Facebook]],<ref>{{Cite news|title=Ricky Martin - Facebook|url=https://www.facebook.com/RickyMartinOfficialPage|publisher=[[Facebook]]|access-date=January 19, 2022|archive-date=January 19, 2022|archive-url=https://ghostarchive.org/archive/20220119190127/https://www.facebook.com/RickyMartinOfficialPage|url-status=live}}</ref> [[YouTube]],<ref>{{Cite news|title=Ricky Martin - YouTube|url=https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCGkkG-VYVXenlhVIqjH-9oA|publisher=YouTube|access-date=January 19, 2022|archive-date=January 19, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119192855/https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCGkkG-VYVXenlhVIqjH-9oA|url-status=live}}</ref> and [[TikTok]].<ref>{{Cite news|title=TikTok oficial de Ricky Martin (@ricky__martin)|url=https://www.tiktok.com/@ricky__martin|publisher=[[Facebook]]|access-date=January 19, 2022|archive-date=January 19, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119192854/https://www.tiktok.com/@ricky__martin|url-status=live}}</ref> He stated about social media that he wishes he had "something as powerful as" them since his debut: "Obviously I like to have direct contact with the public, with the media. It's extremely important, but today, from my home, I can talk to millions of people and see their immediate reaction."<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.tvynovelas.com/mx/en-exclusiva/ricky-martin-superar-odio-redes-sociales/|title=¿Qué hace Ricky Martin para superar el odio en las redes sociales?|work=[[TVyNovelas]]|language=es|access-date=January 19, 2022|archive-date=March 21, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200321131734/https://www.tvynovelas.com/mx/en-exclusiva/ricky-martin-superar-odio-redes-sociales/|url-status=dead}}</ref> He is noticed for his friendly interactions with his fans, who are called "[[List of fandom names|Sexy Souls]]".<ref name="Hola Hotel"/><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.canalnet.tv/espectaculos/ricky-martin-sorprendio-a-una-fan-argentina-con-un-tierno-gesto_20210219/|title=Ricky Martin sorprendió a una fan argentina con un tierno gesto|publisher=[[Net TV (Argentina)|Net TV]]|language=es|date=February 19, 2021|access-date=January 19, 2022|archive-date=January 19, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119192925/https://www.canalnet.tv/espectaculos/ricky-martin-sorprendio-a-una-fan-argentina-con-un-tierno-gesto_20210219/|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.musicbusinessworldwide.com/meet-hybe-backed-fave-a-social-marketplace-for-fans-of-bts-and-taylor-swift/|title=100 die hard fans are just as powerful as somebody with 100 million followers on Instagram|publisher=[[Music Business Worldwide]]|last=Needham|first=Jack|date=September 23, 2021|access-date=January 19, 2022|archive-date=January 19, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119192922/https://www.musicbusinessworldwide.com/meet-hybe-backed-fave-a-social-marketplace-for-fans-of-bts-and-taylor-swift/|url-status=live}}</ref> Wax statues of Martin are on display at the [[Madame Tussauds]] wax museums in [[Madame Tussauds San Francisco|San Francisco]], [[Madame Tussauds Sydney|Sydney]], and [[Madame Tussauds#Orlando|Orlando]]. The last one was moved from [[Madame Tussauds Las Vegas|Las Vegas]] to Orlando for the opening of the museum in spring 2015.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.123rf.com/photo_133368855_san-francisco-may-12-2010-wax-statue-of-ricky-martin-wearing-a-pride-flag-at-madame-tussauds-san-fra.html|title=San Francisco - May 12, 2010: Wax Statue of Ricky Martin wearing a Pride flag at Madame Tussauds San Francisco|publisher=[[123RF]]|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 19, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119023121/https://www.billboard.com/music/music-news/ricky-martin-vida-2014-billboard-music-awards-6084953/|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://people.com/celebrity/celebrity-wax-figures-jason-derulo-katy-perry-kendall-jenner/|title=Celebrity Wax Figures That'll Have You Seeing Double|work=People|date=September 17, 2021|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 19, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119023121/https://www.billboard.com/music/music-news/ricky-martin-vida-2014-billboard-music-awards-6084953/|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/latin/latin-artists-madame-tussauds-wax-figures-9644230/|title=All the Latin Music Stars Who Have a Madame Tussauds Wax Figure|magazine=Billboard|last=Roiz|first=Jessica|date=October 12, 2021|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 19, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119023121/https://www.billboard.com/music/music-news/ricky-martin-vida-2014-billboard-music-awards-6084953/|url-status=live}}</ref>

===Fashion===
Martin is considered to be a [[sex symbol]],<ref name="NY Times Party">{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/10/10/arts/music/review-ricky-martin-has-a-unity-party-at-the-garden.html|title=Review: Ricky Martin Has a Unity Party at the Garden|work=The New York Times|first=Jon|last=Pareles|date=October 9, 2015|access-date=May 15, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://people.com/music/ricky-martin-coming-out-gay-extremely-painful/|title=Ricky Martin Opens Up About His Decision to Come Out: 'It Was Extremely Painful for Me'|work=[[People (magazine)|People]] |last=Eisenbrand|first=Katherine|date=January 18, 2018|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120145953/https://people.com/music/ricky-martin-coming-out-gay-extremely-painful/|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://people.com/music/ricky-martin-husband-jwan-yosef-love-at-first-sight/|title=Ricky Martin Admits to Love at First Sight with Husband Jwan Yosef: 'I Lost My Breath'|work=People|last=Boucher|first=Phil|date=March 29, 2018|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120145952/https://people.com/music/ricky-martin-husband-jwan-yosef-love-at-first-sight/|url-status=live}}</ref> and journalists describe him as "the Latin heartthrob".<ref name="ET20"/><ref>{{cite news|url=https://etcanada.com/news/746120/ricky-martin-named-national-spokesperson-for-onepulse-foundation/|title=Ricky Martin Named National Spokesperson For onePulse Foundation|work=[[Entertainment Tonight Canada]]|last=Darmon|first=Aynslee|date=February 11, 2021|access-date=January 20, 2022}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/entertainment/ricky-martin-wants-to-wed/2015/05/27/328b8610-042f-11e5-93f4-f24d4af7f97d_story.html|title=Ricky Martin wants to wed|newspaper=The Washington Post|date=May 27, 2015|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120150025/https://www.washingtonpost.com/entertainment/ricky-martin-wants-to-wed/2015/05/27/328b8610-042f-11e5-93f4-f24d4af7f97d_story.html|url-status=live}}</ref> His fashion and style evolution, from "as '80s as you'd expect" during his time with Menudo to "a style groove, often opting for sharp, tailored suits with clean lines" since 2009, has been noticed by the media.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.huffpost.com/entry/ricky-martin-style-evolution_n_5a68a6c5e4b00228300890a4|title=Ricky Martin's Style Evolution, From Menudo To Mullets And Beyond|work=HuffPost|last=Brucculieri|first=Julia|date=January 25, 2018|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120150102/https://www.huffpost.com/entry/ricky-martin-style-evolution_n_5a68a6c5e4b00228300890a4|url-status=live}}</ref> Natalia Trejo from ''¡Hola!'' described him as "one of the most stylish Latin men in the entertainment industry", highlighting his "baggy leather pants", "tailored suits", and "color-block blazers" that have marked "some of the noteworthy trends of each decade". The reviewer also commented that Martin is "an example of mixing business with casual" and has "always had a personal sense of style".<ref name="Hola Fashion">{{cite news|url=https://www.hola.com/us/fashion/20200508fn7lewfd37/ricky-martin-style-evolution-pictures-1/|title=Ricky Martin's Style Evolution – from the late '80s to early '00s, and more|work=¡Hola!|last=Trejo|first=Natalia|date=May 8, 2020|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120150107/https://www.hola.com/us/fashion/20200508fn7lewfd37/ricky-martin-style-evolution-pictures-1/|url-status=live}}</ref> [[JD Institute of Fashion Technology]] views Martin as a [[fashion icon]], praising him for "pushing the fashion boundaries with every new look".<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.jdinstitute.edu.in/fashion-icons-who-are-making-sensational-statements/|title=Fashion Icons Who Are Making Sensational Statements|publisher=[[JD Institute of Fashion Technology]]|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120150240/https://www.jdinstitute.edu.in/fashion-icons-who-are-making-sensational-statements/|url-status=live}}</ref> In 1997, he went on the cover of ''[[People en Español]]''{{'}}s first edition of 25 Most Beautiful; he has since "been a constant presence" on their 25 or 50 Most Beautiful lists.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://peopleenespanol.com/gallery/50-most-beautiful-covers-people-espanol-bellos-through-years/?slide=240541#240541|title=50 Most Beautiful|work=People en Español|date=December 22, 2014|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120150215/https://peopleenespanol.com/gallery/50-most-beautiful-covers-people-espanol-bellos-through-years/?slide=240541|url-status=live}}</ref> Two years later, he was featured on the cover of both ''Rolling Stone'' and ''[[Time (magazine)|Time]]'' magazines.<ref name="HRCup"/><ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-lists/1999-rolling-stone-covers-216141/|title=1999 Rolling Stone Covers|magazine=Rolling Stone|date=May 12, 2004|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120150216/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-lists/1999-rolling-stone-covers-216141/|url-status=live}}</ref>

Martin is considered to be one of the sexiest men in the world, according to various publications.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.lacapital.com.ar/escenario/el-video-ricky-martin-tocandose-estallo-instagram-n2547523.html|title=El video de Ricky Martin tocándose estalló en Instagram|work=[[La Capital]]|language=es|date=December 4, 2019|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120150714/https://www.lacapital.com.ar/escenario/el-video-ricky-martin-tocandose-estallo-instagram-n2547523.html|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.hola.com/us-es/celebrities/galeria/2019080226099/ricky-martin-tatuajes-lado-espiritual-mz/1/|title=Ricky Martin muestra su lado espiritual a través de sus tatuajes|work=¡Hola!|language=es|date=August 2, 2019|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120150311/https://www.hola.com/us-es/celebrities/galeria/2019080226099/ricky-martin-tatuajes-lado-espiritual-mz/1/|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://peru.com/entretenimiento/celebrities/ricky-martin-hermano-cantante-enloquece-instagram-cuerpo-infarto-noticia-560765/|title=Ricky Martin: hermano del cantante enloquece Instagram con cuerpo de infarto|publisher=Peru.com|language=es|date=April 11, 2018|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120150320/https://peru.com/entretenimiento/celebrities/ricky-martin-hermano-cantante-enloquece-instagram-cuerpo-infarto-noticia-560765/|url-status=live}}</ref> In 2012, he was voted the sexiest man alive on Broadway.com.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.out.com/entertainment/popnography/2012/11/19/ricky-martin-named-broadways-sexiest-man|title=Ricky Martin Named Broadway's Sexiest Man|work=Out|last=Kinser|first=Jeremy|date=November 19, 2012|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120150333/https://www.out.com/entertainment/popnography/2012/11/19/ricky-martin-named-broadways-sexiest-man|url-status=live}}</ref> The following year, [[VH1]] ranked him as the 28th Sexiest Artist of All Time, stating: "Ricky looks like the model in the magazine ads you stare at in awe thinking, 'There's no way he's that perfect in person'."<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.vh1.com/news/1187/vh1-100-sexiest-artists-complete-list/|title=VH1's 100 Sexiest Artists [Complete List]|publisher=[[VH1]]|last=Viera|first=Bené|date=March 5, 2013|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120150412/http://www.vh1.com/news/1187/vh1-100-sexiest-artists-complete-list/|url-status=live}}</ref> In 2014, ''[[Entertainment Tonight]]'' listed him among the Sexiest Men Alive,<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.etonline.com/slideshow/gallery/154104_sexiest_men_honorable_mentions/21227|title=Sexiest Men Alive: The Best of the Rest|work=Entertainment Tonight|date=November 18, 2014|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120150404/https://www.etonline.com/slideshow/gallery/154104_sexiest_men_honorable_mentions/21227|url-status=live}}</ref> while ''Revista Estilo'' placed him on the list of "the 10 Sexiest Singers" in 2016.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.revistaestilo.net/galeria/gestilodevida/938933-445/los-10-cantantes-mas-sexy?i=11|title=Los 10 Cantantes Mas Sexy|work=Revista Estilo|language=es|last=Gómez|first=Claudia|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120150414/https://www.revistaestilo.net/galeria/gestilodevida/938933-445/los-10-cantantes-mas-sexy?i=11|url-status=live}}</ref> He was ranked at number 16 on the list of "the 50 Hottest Men of All Time" by ''[[Harper's Bazaar]]'' in 2018, being the only Latin man on their list.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.harpersbazaar.com/culture/features/g4612/hottest-men-of-all-time/?slide=16|title=The 50 Hottest Men Of All Time|work=[[Harper's Bazaar]]|last=Fisher|first=Lauren Alexis|date=January 12, 2018|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120150507/https://www.harpersbazaar.com/culture/features/g4612/hottest-men-of-all-time/?slide=16|url-status=live}}</ref> In 2019, [[TN (TV channel)|TN]] described Martin as "the sexiest man in the world".<ref>{{cite news|url=https://tn.com.ar/musica/noticias/2019/12/04/ricky-martin-publico-un-provocador-video-y-sus-fans-enloquecieron/|title=Ricky Martin publicó un provocador video y sus fans enloquecieron|publisher=TN|language=es|date=December 4, 2019|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120150448/https://tn.com.ar/musica/noticias/2019/12/04/ricky-martin-publico-un-provocador-video-y-sus-fans-enloquecieron/|url-status=live}}</ref> He has been noted for looking younger than his age,<ref name="HRCup"/> with ''Billboard''{{'}}s Chris Payne labeling him "ageless".<ref name="Billboard Vida Performance"/> The singer has attended several [[fashion show]]s, including the [[Giorgio Armani]] show at [[Milan Fashion Week]] in 2011,<ref name="Hola Fashion"/> the [[Marc Jacobs]] show in 2013,<ref name="Hola Fashion"/> the [[Berluti]] menswear spring-summer 2020 show at [[Paris Fashion Week]],<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/gallery/see-all-stars-front-row-at-paris-mens-fashion-week-1219794/4-jwan-yosef-and-ricky-martin/|title=See all the Stars Front Row at Paris Men's Fashion Week|work=The Hollywood Reporter|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120150811/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/gallery/see-all-stars-front-row-at-paris-mens-fashion-week-1219794/4-jwan-yosef-and-ricky-martin/|url-status=live}}</ref> the [[Dior]] men's pre-fall 2020 show,<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.thecut.com/2019/12/dior-miami-art-basel-show-review.html|title=Every Celebrity Was at the Dior Show|work=[[New York (magazine)#The Cut|The Cut]]|last=Petrarca|first=Emilia|date=December 4, 2019|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120150526/https://www.thecut.com/2019/12/dior-miami-art-basel-show-review.html|url-status=live}}</ref> and the [[Virgil Abloh]] Spring-Summer 2022 show held by [[Louis Vuitton]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.etonline.com/kanye-west-and-kim-kardashian-reunite-to-pay-respects-to-virgil-abloh-at-final-louis-vuitton-show|title=Kanye West and Kim Kardashian Reunite to Pay Respects to Virgil Abloh at Final Louis Vuitton Show|work=Entertainment Tonight|last=Pierre|first=Mekishana|date=November 30, 2021|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120150552/https://www.etonline.com/kanye-west-and-kim-kardashian-reunite-to-pay-respects-to-virgil-abloh-at-final-louis-vuitton-show|url-status=live}}</ref>

==Personal life==
===Sexual orientation and early relationships===
According to an interview with ''Rolling Stone'' in 1999, Martin experienced his first kiss at age 13 and lost his virginity at age 14 in Argentina.<ref name="RS Nancy"/> In 1990, shortly after he had arrived in Mexico to star in ''Mama Ama el Rock'', he met a woman, who was the host of a television show. They began dating quickly and broke up a few months later. In 1992, he fell in love with Mexican singer [[Alejandra Guzmán]], who was separated from her husband at the time. They began dating until Guzmán returned to her husband and pretended Martin was her assistant on a phone call, while she was sleeping with her husband. In an interview with Univision, Martin admitted that she broke his heart.<ref name="rickybook"/><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.show.news/music/Romperia-Alejandra-Guzman-el-corazon-de-Ricky-Martin-revela-20201130-0001.html|title=Rompería Alejandra Guzmán el corazón de Ricky Martin, revela|publisher=Show News|last=Rodríguez|first=Sayra|language=es|date=November 30, 2020|access-date=January 21, 2022|archive-date=January 21, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121191018/https://www.show.news/music/Romperia-Alejandra-Guzman-el-corazon-de-Ricky-Martin-revela-20201130-0001.html|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.terra.com.mx/entretenimiento/2021/12/19/ricky-martin-parejas-del-cantante-antes-de-caer-en-los-brazos-de-jwan-yosef-22030.html|title=Ricky Martin: 5 parejas del cantante antes de caer en los brazos de Jwan Yosef|publisher=[[Terra (company)|Terra]]|language=es|date=December 19, 2021|access-date=January 21, 2022|archive-date=January 21, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121191029/https://www.terra.com.mx/entretenimiento/2021/12/19/ricky-martin-parejas-del-cantante-antes-de-caer-en-los-brazos-de-jwan-yosef-22030.html|url-status=live}}</ref> In the same year, Martin was rumored to have a relationship with Argentine tennis player [[Gabriela Sabatini]]. Sabatini's sister-in-law, [[Catherine Fulop]], confirmed the rumor in 2020.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.hola.com/us-es/celebrities/20200302fl6o64xfyw/ricky-martin-romance-gabriela-sabatini/|title=Ricky Martin Tuvo Un Romance Con Un Famosa Tenista Argentina|work=¡Hola!|last=Collantes|first=Alonso|language=es|date=March 2, 2020|access-date=January 21, 2022|archive-date=January 21, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121191052/https://www.hola.com/us-es/celebrities/20200302fl6o64xfyw/ricky-martin-romance-gabriela-sabatini/|url-status=live}}</ref> During the time he was playing in ''General Hospital'', he met a "very handsome" man at a radio station, "stopped fearing [his] sexuality", and started dating him. Martin's mother supported him when she discovered that he was in love with a man, saying: "I love you, my son, I'm so happy for you. Bring it on. I'm right behind you." However, after the relationship ended, Martin "locked [his] feelings even deeper inside" and began dating women again. He recalls: "I already felt it was hard to be a Latino in Hollywood; what could have been more difficult than being Latino and gay?"<ref name="rickybook"/><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.pinknews.co.uk/2010/12/13/ricky-martin-my-mother-helped-me-come-out/|title=Ricky Martin: My mother helped me come out|work=[[PinkNews]]|date=December 13, 2010|access-date=January 21, 2022|archive-date=January 21, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121191103/https://www.pinknews.co.uk/2010/12/13/ricky-martin-my-mother-helped-me-come-out/|url-status=live}}</ref> Martin began dating Mexican television host [[Rebecca de Alba]] in 1994; they were in an [[On-again, off-again relationship|on-and-off relationship]] until 2005. In May 2021, Alba revealed that she became pregnant several times in her life, but [[Miscarriage|lost]] all of the pregnancies, expressing that one of them was from Martin. Martin also had relationships with Lilly Melgar, Adriana Biega, Maital Saban, and Inés Misan during his break-up times with Alba in the late 1990s and early 2000s. He declared that "there was chemistry with them" and he "wasn't fooling anyone".<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.milenio.com/espectaculos/famosos/rebecca-alba-revela-perdio-bebes-ricky-martin|title='Lo perdimos': Rebecca de Alba revela que perdió varios bebés; uno de ellos de Ricky Martin|work=[[Milenio]]|language=es|date=May 2, 2021|access-date=January 21, 2022|archive-date=January 21, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121191103/https://www.milenio.com/espectaculos/famosos/rebecca-alba-revela-perdio-bebes-ricky-martin|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.pinknews.co.uk/2018/04/23/who-has-ricky-martin-dated-open-relationships-madonna-gay-marriage/|title=Who has Ricky Martin dated? From a rumoured fling with Madonna to being a gay father of two|work=PinkNews|last=Finamore|first=Emma|date=April 23, 2010|access-date=January 21, 2022|archive-date=January 21, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121191557/https://www.pinknews.co.uk/2018/04/23/who-has-ricky-martin-dated-open-relationships-madonna-gay-marriage/|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.univision.com/famosos/ricky-martin-homosexualidad-barbara-walters-entrevista|title=Ricky Martin dice que no quiso engañar a nadie cuando salió con mujeres en su juventud|publisher=Univision|language=es|date=June 2, 2021|access-date=January 21, 2022|archive-date=January 21, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121191551/https://www.univision.com/famosos/ricky-martin-homosexualidad-barbara-walters-entrevista|url-status=live}}</ref>

In August 2008, Martin became a father to twin boys named Matteo and Valentino, born via [[Surrogacy#Gestational surrogacy|gestational surrogacy]]. He explained that he chose surrogacy to become a parent for being "intriguing and faster" than adoption, which was complicated and could take a long time.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://people.com/parents/ricky-martin-welcomes-twin-boys/|title=Ricky Martin Welcomes Twin Boys|work=People|last=Laudadio|first=Marisa|date=August 20, 2008|access-date=January 21, 2022|archive-date=January 21, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121191557/https://people.com/parents/ricky-martin-welcomes-twin-boys/|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://people.com/parents/first-photo-of-ricky-martins-twins/|title=First Photo of Ricky Martin's Twins!|work=People|last=Wihlborg|first=Ulrica|date=December 10, 2008|access-date=January 21, 2022|archive-date=January 21, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121191603/https://people.com/parents/first-photo-of-ricky-martins-twins/|url-status=live}}</ref> In March 2010, Martin publicly [[Coming out|came out]] as gay via a message on his website, stating: "I am proud to say that I am a fortunate homosexual man. I am very blessed to be who I am."<ref name="People Reveal">{{cite news|url=https://people.com/celebrity/ricky-martin-reveals-hes-gay/|title=Ricky Martin Reveals He's Gay|work=People|last=Donaldson-evans|first=Catherine|date=March 29, 2010|access-date=January 21, 2022|archive-date=January 21, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121191826/https://people.com/celebrity/ricky-martin-reveals-hes-gay/|url-status=live}}</ref> Years later, he revealed that although his music was "heard all over the world" and he "could high five God" in 1999, he "wasn't living to the fullest" and was sad and depressed.<ref name="Variety Come out"/> He kept asking himself, "Am I gay? Am I bisexual? Am I confused? What am I?", explaining: "Sexuality is one complicated thing. It's not black and white. It's filled with colors. When I was dating women, I was in love with women. It felt right, it felt beautiful."<ref name="People No Secrets"/> In an interview with ''[[Vanity Fair (magazine)|Vanity Fair]]'', he declared: "There was love, passion. I do not regret anything, any of the relationships I lived, they taught me a lot, both men and women."<ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://www.revistavanityfair.es/la-revista/articulos/exclusiva-ricky-martin-su-novio-y-sus-hijos-en-una-sesio-n-de-fotos-u-nica/16297|title=La nueva vida de Ricky|magazine=Vanity Fair|language=es|last=Riego|first=Marta del|date=March 21, 2012|access-date=January 21, 2022|archive-date=January 21, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121191811/https://www.revistavanityfair.es/la-revista/articulos/exclusiva-ricky-martin-su-novio-y-sus-hijos-en-una-sesio-n-de-fotos-u-nica/16297|url-status=live}}</ref> Martin also told ''Fama!'': "I know that I like both men and women, I'm against sexual labels, we are simply human beings with emotional and sexual needs. I like to enjoy sex in total freedom, so I'm open to having sex with a woman if I feel desire." Despite this, he expressed that he wouldn't be interested in "an ongoing relationship with a woman", stating: "Men are my thing".<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.advocate.com/people/2016/1/19/ricky-martin-open-sex-women-doesnt-call-himself-bi|title=Ricky Martin 'Open' to Sex With Women, But Doesn't Call Himself Bi|work=[[Attitude (magazine)|Attitude]]|last=Ring|first=Trudy|date=January 19, 2016|access-date=January 21, 2022|archive-date=January 21, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121191905/https://www.advocate.com/people/2016/1/19/ricky-martin-open-sex-women-doesnt-call-himself-bi|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.advocate.com/commentary/2016/1/25/ricky-martin-bi-closet|title=Is Ricky Martin in the Bi Closet?|work=Attitude|last=Szymanski|first=Mike|date=January 25, 2016|access-date=January 21, 2022|archive-date=January 21, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121191838/https://www.advocate.com/commentary/2016/1/25/ricky-martin-bi-closet|url-status=live}}</ref> In 2000, American broadcast journalist [[Barbara Walters]] asked Martin about his sexuality on national television: "You could stop these rumors. You could say, 'Yes I am gay or no I'm not.'" In 2021, Martin, who had answered with "I just don't feel like it" at the time, revealed that her question had made him "felt violated", since he "was just not ready to come out" and was "very afraid"; he said that it resulted in "a little [[Post-traumatic stress disorder|PTSD]]" that "still haunts him".<ref name="People No Secrets"/> Martin dated Puerto Rican economist Carlos González Abella from 2010 to 2014, as his first relationship with a man after coming out as gay.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://people.com/parents/ricky-martin-wants-more-kids-girls-wwhl/|title=Ricky Martin Reveals He Wants More Kids — and He's Picking Girls This Time|work=People|last=Quinn|first=Dave|date=February 23, 2017|access-date=January 21, 2022|archive-date=January 21, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121191735/https://people.com/parents/ricky-martin-wants-more-kids-girls-wwhl/|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.latintimes.com/ricky-martin-back-ex-carlos-gonzalez-abella-or-are-they-just-friends-291215|title=Is Ricky Martin Back With Ex Carlos González Abella Or Are They Just Friends?|work=Latin Times|date=January 27, 2015|access-date=January 21, 2022|archive-date=January 21, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121191750/https://www.latintimes.com/ricky-martin-back-ex-carlos-gonzalez-abella-or-are-they-just-friends-291215|url-status=live}}</ref>

===Marriage===
[[File:Ricky Martin Jwan Yosef Golden Globe Awards 2018 (cropped).jpg|thumb|right|upright=1|Martin and [[Jwan Yosef]] at the [[75th Golden Globe Awards|2018 Golden Globe Awards]]]]
Syrian-Swedish painter [[Jwan Yosef]] shared a photo of himself and Martin on Instagram on March 30, 2016, with the caption: "Obviously we're starting a band."<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.instagram.com/jwanyosef/p/BDlWrdgL2ci|title=Obviously we're starting a band #tokyo #meijijingu|author-link=Jwan Yosef|last=Yosef|first=Jwan|via=Instagram|access-date=January 23, 2022|date=March 30, 2016|url-status=live|archive-date=January 23, 2022|archive-url=https://ghostarchive.org/archive/20220123200112/https://www.instagram.com/jwanyosef/p/BDlWrdgL2ci/}}</ref> Soon it was rumored that Yosef is Martin's new boyfriend.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.elheraldo.hn/entretenimiento/945357-466/conoce-a-jwan-yosef-el-nuevo-novio-de-ricky-martin|title=Conoce a Jwan Yosef, el nuevo novio de Ricky Martin|work=El Heraldo|language=es|date=March 31, 2016|access-date=January 23, 2022|archive-date=January 23, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220123202753/https://www.elheraldo.hn/entretenimiento/945357-466/conoce-a-jwan-yosef-el-nuevo-novio-de-ricky-martin|url-status=live}}</ref> Martin confirmed their relationship on April 18, 2016, and they made their red carpet debut as a couple at the [[amfAR]] Inspiration Gala.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://people.com/celebrity/ricky-martin-and-jwan-yosef-make-red-carpet-debut/|title=Ricky Martin and New Boyfriend Jwan Yosef Make Red Carpet Debut in Sao Paolo|work=People|last=Mizoguchi|first=Karen|date=April 18, 2016|access-date=January 23, 2022|archive-date=January 23, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220123202758/https://people.com/celebrity/ricky-martin-and-jwan-yosef-make-red-carpet-debut/|url-status=live}}</ref> Martin later revealed that he met Yosef on Instagram and they "were talking for like six months without [him] hearing his voice". Subsequently, Martin went to London, where Yosef was living, and they met each other.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://people.com/music/ricky-martin-fiance-jwan-yosef-instagram/|title=You'll Never Guess Where Ricky Martin Met Fiancé Jwan Yosef (Spoiler: On Instagram!)|work=People|last=Adams|first=Char|date=February 17, 2017|access-date=January 23, 2022|archive-date=January 23, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220123202806/https://people.com/music/ricky-martin-fiance-jwan-yosef-instagram/|url-status=live}}</ref> On November 15, 2016, during an interview on ''[[The Ellen Show]]'', he announced that he has proposed to Yosef and they are engaged.<ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/latin/ricky-martin-engaged-jwan-yosef-7580444/|title=Ricky Martin Announces Engagement to Jwan Yosef|magazine=Billboard|last=Penrose|first=Nerisha|date=November 16, 2016|access-date=January 23, 2022|archive-date=January 23, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220123202934/https://www.billboard.com/music/latin/ricky-martin-engaged-jwan-yosef-7580444/|url-status=live}}</ref> In January 2018, Martin confirmed that he has secretly married Yosef: "I'm a husband, but we're doing a heavy party in a couple of months, I'll let you know."<ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/music-news/ricky-martin-jwan-yosef-are-married-8093813/|title=Ricky Martin & Jwan Yosef Are Married|magazine=Billboard|last=Aniftos|first=Rania|date=January 10, 2018|access-date=January 23, 2022|archive-date=January 23, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220123202931/https://www.billboard.com/music/music-news/ricky-martin-jwan-yosef-are-married-8093813/|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/music-news/music-secret-marriages-cardi-b-ricky-martin-8462905/|title=11 Secret Music Marriages, From Cardi B & Offset to Beyonce & Jay-Z|magazine=Billboard|last=Mele|first=Sofia|date=June 26, 2018|access-date=January 23, 2022|archive-date=January 23, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220123202937/https://www.billboard.com/music/music-news/music-secret-marriages-cardi-b-ricky-martin-8462905/|url-status=live}}</ref> On December 31, 2018, they announced that they have welcomed their first daughter together, named Lucia Martin-Yosef.<ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/latin/ricky-martin-baby-girl-lucia-birth-announcement-photo-8491985/|title=Ricky Martin & Husband Welcome Baby Girl to the Family'|magazine=Billboard|last=Iasimone|first=Ashley|date=December 31, 2018|access-date=January 23, 2022|archive-date=January 23, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220123203039/https://www.billboard.com/music/latin/ricky-martin-baby-girl-lucia-birth-announcement-photo-8491985/|url-status=live}}</ref> Martin later explained that Lucia was born on December 24, coinciding with his 47th birthday.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.hola.com/us/celebrities/20191115fiec3d2tuh/ricky-martin-fatherhood-four-children/|title=Ricky Martin On Becoming A Dad At 47 And How His Daughter Rules The Household|work=¡Hola!|last=Garcías|first=Cynthia|date=November 15, 2019|access-date=January 23, 2022|archive-date=January 23, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220123203002/https://www.hola.com/us/celebrities/20191115fiec3d2tuh/ricky-martin-fatherhood-four-children/|url-status=live}}</ref> In September 2019, while accepting an award at the 23rd annual [[Human Rights Campaign]] (HRC) National Dinner, he announced that they are expecting their fourth child.<ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/latin/ricky-martin-husband-jwan-yosef-expecting-their-fourth-child-together-8531666/|title=Ricky Martin & Husband Expecting Fourth Child Together: Watch the Special Announcement|magazine=Billboard|last=Peters|first=Mitchell|date=September 29, 2019|access-date=January 23, 2022|archive-date=January 23, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220123203005/https://www.billboard.com/music/latin/ricky-martin-husband-jwan-yosef-expecting-their-fourth-child-together-8531666/|url-status=live}}</ref> On October 29, 2019, he shared a photo of himself, Yosef, and their new-born son, named Renn Martin-Yosef, with the caption: "Our son Renn Martin-Yosef has been born."<ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/latin/ricky-martin-jwan-yosef-baby-renn-8541392/|title=Ricky Martin & Husband Jwan Yosef Welcome Fourth Baby|magazine=Billboard|last=Fernandez|first=Suzette|date=January 18, 2018|access-date=January 23, 2022|archive-date=January 23, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220123204130/https://www.billboard.com/music/latin/ricky-martin-jwan-yosef-baby-renn-8541392/|url-status=live}}</ref>

===Beliefs and religion===
During an interview with ''People'' in 2002, Martin expressed that he believes in "love", "the power of healing", and "God", thanks to his parents.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://people.com/celebrity/ricky-martin-recognized-for-good-works/|title=Ricky Martin Recognized for Good Works|work=People|last1=Stephen M.|first1=Silverman|last2=Susan|first2=Mandel|date=September 23, 2002|access-date=January 24, 2022|archive-date=January 24, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220124170042/https://people.com/celebrity/ricky-martin-recognized-for-good-works/|url-status=live}}</ref> The name he chose for his son Matteo means "gift from God".<ref>{{cite news|url=https://people.com/parents/ricky-martin-introduces-valentino-matteo/|title=Ricky Martin Introduces Twins Valentino and Matteo|work=People|date=December 15, 2008|access-date=January 24, 2022|archive-date=January 24, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220124170023/https://people.com/parents/ricky-martin-introduces-valentino-matteo/|url-status=live}}</ref> According to his statements in a 2021 interview, he still believes in God.<ref name="Buena Vida God">{{cite news|url=https://buenavida.pr/ricky-martin-enfocado-en-el-bienestar/|title=Ricky Martin, Enfocado en el Bienestar|work=[[Casiano Communications|Buena Vida]]|language=es|last=Martín|first=Nedda S. Perales|date=August 11, 2021|access-date=January 24, 2022|archive-date=January 24, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220124170040/https://buenavida.pr/ricky-martin-enfocado-en-el-bienestar/|url-status=live}}</ref> He was raised Catholic but he said is not "the person who would ever look down upon one religion". He expressed that he also admires and likes [[Buddhist philosophy]], but does not subscribe to the religion, since if he does, he cannot "be of anything else"; he does not want to be limited in certain aspects and follow a religion's specific rules. He tries to remain "open to everything" and makes "a concerted effort to always find new teachings and new paths" everywhere he goes and in every situation he finds himself in. Martin believes that everyone can "decide what makes them happy" and although "everyone needs to accept the life they were given", it does not mean they "should not live it as fully as possible".<ref name="rickybook"/><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/india/i-like-buddhist-philosophy-ricky-martin/story-0z03q2CqfpZBSio52xcVGL.html|title=I like Buddhist philosophy: Ricky Martin|work=[[Hindustan Times]]|date=November 28, 2006|access-date=January 24, 2022|archive-date=January 24, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220124170037/https://www.hindustantimes.com/india/i-like-buddhist-philosophy-ricky-martin/story-0z03q2CqfpZBSio52xcVGL.html|url-status=live}}</ref>

===Health and sports===
Martin began practicing [[yoga]] after a trip to Thailand in 1997.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.people.com/people/archive/article/0,,20133136,00.html|title=Ricky Martin : Zen and Now|work=People|last=Tresniowski|first=Alex|date=December 4, 2000|access-date=August 1, 2012|archive-date=April 5, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140405080326/http://www.people.com/people/archive/article/0,,20133136,00.html|url-status=dead}}</ref> He also began practicing [[meditation]] following a trip to India.<ref name="Vogue Skin">{{cite news|url=https://www.vogue.com/article/ricky-martin-beauty-secrets|title=Ricky Martin Reveals His Daily Skin-Care and Wellness Routine|work=[[Vogue (magazine)|Vogue]]|last=Ruffner|first=Zoe|date=July 28, 2021|access-date=January 24, 2022|archive-date=January 24, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220124170052/https://www.vogue.com/article/ricky-martin-beauty-secrets|url-status=live}}</ref> In 2021, he explained that he gets up every morning at 5:30, before his family and puts himself in a [[lotus position]] and oxygenates his body. He also expressed that has a gym in his house, saying: "If I have space to see myself in the mirror and put on my products, then I also have to have space for my body."<ref name="Buena Vida God"/> During an appearance on ''[[The Dr. Oz Show]]'' in 2017, Martin revealed that he "was diagnosed with high cholesterol" at age 18. Although he did not pay attention to the high cholesterol at the time, it made him decide to become a [[Vegetarianism|vegetarian]] since 2013 to reduce cholesterol, despite loving meat as "a Latin man".<ref>{{cite news|url=https://peopleenespanol.com/celebridades/ricky-martin-lucha-contra-colesterol/|title=Ricky Martin revela el culpable de que sea vegetariano|work=People en Español|language=es|last=Trejos|first=Carolina|date=February 22, 2017|access-date=January 24, 2022|archive-date=January 24, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220124170111/https://peopleenespanol.com/celebridades/ricky-martin-lucha-contra-colesterol/|url-status=live}}</ref> In 2020, he opened up that he suffered from [[anxiety]] for the first time in his life, following the [[COVID-19 lockdowns]], stating that making music became his "medicine".<ref name="Pausa AP"/>

===Real estate===
In March 2001, Martin purchased a 7,082-square-foot house in [[Miami Beach, Florida|Miami Beach]] for $6.4 million; he sold the unit for $10.6 million in 2005.<ref name="Variety House">{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2007/dirt/real-estalker/ricky-martin-selling-miami-mansion-1201226468/|title=Ricky Martin Selling Miami Mansion|work=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|last=David|first=Mark|date=July 23, 2007|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120192535/https://variety.com/2007/dirt/real-estalker/ricky-martin-selling-miami-mansion-1201226468/|url-status=live}}</ref> In September 2004, he paid $11.9 million for an 11,000-square-foot Mediterranean-style villa in Los Angeles, which he sold in 2006 for $15 million.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-2004-sep-19-re-hotprop19-story.html|title=Ricky Martin Opens Up About His Decision to Come Out: 'It Was Extremely Painful for Me'|work=[[Los Angeles Times]]|last=Ryon|first=Ruth|author-link=Ruth Ryon|date=September 19, 2004|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=March 6, 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210306092945/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-2004-sep-19-re-hotprop19-story.html|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="Forbes House">{{cite news|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/trulia/2016/12/06/ricky-martin-drops-millions-on-a-beverly-hills-mansion/?sh=45a753af2f33|title=Ricky Martin Drops Millions On A Beverly Hills Mansion|work=[[Forbes]]|date=December 6, 2016|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120192556/https://www.forbes.com/sites/trulia/2016/12/06/ricky-martin-drops-millions-on-a-beverly-hills-mansion/?sh=45a753af2f33|url-status=live}}</ref> In May 2005, he purchased a 9,491-square-foot house in Miami Beach for $10 million; he sold the villa for $10.6 million in 2012. In 2007, he paid $16.2 million for a mansion in [[Golden Beach, Florida|Golden Beach]]. He sold the property in 2012 for $12.8 million, incurring a loss.<ref name="Variety House"/><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.huffpost.com/entry/ricky-martin-sells-golden-beach-home_n_2167391|title=Ricky Martin Sells Golden Beach Mansion For $12.8 Million (Photos)|work=[[Huffington Post]]|date=November 20, 2012|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120192627/https://www.huffpost.com/entry/ricky-martin-sells-golden-beach-home_n_2167391|url-status=live}}</ref> In the same year, he bought a 3,147-square-foot [[condominium]] in New York City for $5.9 million; he sold the condo for $7.1 million in 2017.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.mansionglobal.com/articles/ricky-martin-cuts-price-of-nyc-condo-by-more-than-1m-to-7-1m-52072|title=Ricky Martin Cuts Price of NYC Condo By More Than $1M to $7.1M|work=[[Dow Jones & Company|Mansion Global]]|date=January 18, 2018|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120192818/https://www.mansionglobal.com/articles/ricky-martin-cuts-price-of-nyc-condo-by-more-than-1m-to-7-1m-52072|url-status=live}}</ref> In 2014, he rented a 900-square-metre mansion in Sydney, which became famous as "the Bronte Wave House" and was sold for $16 million in May 2015, marking one of the most expensive properties sold in the city that year.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.stuff.co.nz/life-style/home-property/66083575/ricky-martins-115-million-sydney-home|title=Ricky Martin's $11.5 million Sydney home|publisher=[[Stuff (website)|Stuff]]|last=Anderson|first=Anna|date=February 12, 2015|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120192650/https://www.stuff.co.nz/life-style/home-property/66083575/ricky-martins-115-million-sydney-home|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.businessinsider.com.au/the-10-most-expensive-properties-sold-in-sydney-this-year-2015-7|title=The 10 most expensive properties sold in Sydney this year|work=[[Business Insider]]|last=Chang|first=Olivia|date=July 13, 2015|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=July 14, 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150714214659/https://www.businessinsider.com.au/the-10-most-expensive-properties-sold-in-sydney-this-year-2015-7|url-status=dead}}</ref> In December 2016, he purchased an 11,300-square-foot mansion in [[Beverly Hills, California|Beverly Hills]]. The estate, which is Martin's current house, has seven bedrooms and eight bathrooms with outdoor seating areas scattered throughout  33,000 square feet. It is a "private getaway in the middle of the city", located up the street from [[the Beverly Hills Hotel]].<ref name="Forbes House"/> Martin also owns a property in Puerto Rico and a private 19.7-acre island in Brazil.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.hellomagazine.com/homes/20210421111523/ricky-martin-home-puerto-rico-inside-photos/|title=Ricky Martin's family home in Puerto Rico is as stylish as it gets|work=[[Hello (magazine)|Hello!]]|last=Murphy|first=Nichola|date=April 21, 2021|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120192643/https://www.hellomagazine.com/homes/20210421111523/ricky-martin-home-puerto-rico-inside-photos/|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://people.com/home/celebrity-private-islands/?slide=6800729#6800729|title=No Trespassing! 16 Celebs Who've Owned Private Islands|work=[[People (magazine)|People]]|last2=Boucher|first2=Phil|last1=Mikelbank|first1=Peter|date=February 18, 2021|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120192645/https://people.com/home/celebrity-private-islands/?slide=6800729#6800729|url-status=live}}</ref> He purchased the latter for $8 million in 2008.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.forbes.com/2008/05/09/stars-second-homes-forbeslife-cx_ls_0509realestate.html|title=Second Homes Of The Stars|work=[[Forbes]]|date=May 9, 2008|access-date=January 20, 2022|archive-date=January 20, 2022|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120192803/https://www.forbes.com/2008/05/09/stars-second-homes-forbeslife-cx_ls_0509realestate.html|url-status=live}}</ref>

==Legacy and influence==
Martin has been regarded as the "[[Honorific nicknames in popular music#M|King of Latin Pop]]" by various publications, such as the Grammy Awards,<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.grammy.com/grammys/news/ricky-martin-host-biggest-night-latin-music-19-years-after-performing-inaugural-show|title=Ricky Martin To Host The Biggest Night In Latin Music 19 Years After Performing At Inaugural Show|last=Yglesias|first=Ana Monroy|publisher=Grammy Awards|date=October 25, 2019|access-date=January 27, 2022}}</ref> ''Billboard'',<ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://www.billboard.com/pro/rihanna-savage-x-fenty-show-vol-3-best-moments/|title=7 Can't-Miss Moments From Rihanna's 'Savage x Fenty Show Vol. 3'|magazine=Billboard|last=Mamo|first=Heran|date=September 23, 2021|access-date=January 27, 2022}}</ref> ''Rolling Stone'',<ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-latin/nathy-peluso-anuel-aa-picks-week-of-may-25th-1004364/|title=RS Latin Music Picks: Week of May 25th|magazine=Rolling Stone|last=Exposito|first=Suzy|date=May 29, 2020|access-date=January 27, 2022}}</ref> ''Time'',<ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://time.com/5526369/grammys-2019-camila-cabello-border-wall/|title=Camila Cabello's Grammy Performance Had a Hidden Anti-Wall Message|magazine=Time|last=Greenspan|first=Rachel E.|date=February 10, 2019|access-date=January 27, 2022}}</ref> ''People'',<ref name="People No Secrets"/> ''[[Vogue (magazine)|Vogue]]'',<ref name="Vogue Skin"/> ''[[The Independent]]'',<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/health-and-families/ricky-martin-same-sex-parenting-b1861706.html|title=Ricky Martin Wants to 'Normalise Families' with Same-Sex Parents|work=[[The Independent]]|last=Abraham|first=Ellie|date=June 8, 2021|access-date=January 27, 2022}}</ref> ''[[Entertainment Weekly]]'',<ref name="EW Voice"/> ''[[Entertainment Tonight Canada]]'',<ref>{{cite news|url=https://etcanada.com/photos/787518/groundbreaking-lgbtq-musicians/#image-787532|title=Groundbreaking LGBTQ+ Musicians|work=Entertainment Tonight Canada|last=Mahjouri|first=Shakiel|date=June 2, 2021|access-date=January 27, 2022}}</ref> [[NBC News]],<ref name="NBC PR"/> and [[ABC News]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://abcnews.go.com/GMA/Culture/video/ricky-martin-opens-family-kids-comfortable-skin-78059287|title=Ricky Martin opens up about his family, kids and being 'more comfortable in his skin'|publisher=ABC News|access-date=January 27, 2022}}</ref> Additionally, he has been referred to as the "King of Latin Music",<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.lafm.com.co/entretenimiento/30-anos-de-ricky-martin-como-solista-cinco-hechos-que-marcaron-vida-del-artista|title=30 años de Ricky Martin como solista: Cinco hechos que marcaron vida del artista|publisher=[[La FM]]|language=es|last=Ruiz|first=Paula|access-date=January 30, 2022|date=November 26, 2021}}</ref> the "Latin Pop God",<ref>{{cite news|url=https://hollywoodlife.com/2021/12/28/ricky-martin-daughter-lucia-birthday-rare-photos/|title=Ricky Martin Shares Rare Photos Of Daughter Lucia, 3, As He Celebrates Her Birthday In Puerto Rico|publisher=Hollywood Life|access-date=December 29, 2021|date=December 28, 2021}}</ref> the "Latin King of Pop",<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.latinpost.com/articles/143117/20200101/everything-you-need-to-know-about-super-bowl-liv.htm|title=Everything You Need to Know About Super Bowl 2020|publisher=Latin Post|last=Vega|first=Carlos Dela|access-date=January 31, 2022|date=January 1, 2020}}</ref> the "Latin American King of Pop",<ref>{{cite news|url=https://elintranews.com/celebrities/2021/06/11/rompe-las-plataformas-ricky-martin-y-paloma-mami-se-vuelven-tendencia-con-su-nuevo-tema-musical/|title=¡Rompe las plataformas! Ricky Martin y Paloma Mami se vuelven tendencia con su nuevo tema musical|publisher=El Intranews|last=Hernandez|first=Larsen|language=es|access-date=February 3, 2022|date=June 11, 2021}}</ref> the "Latin King",<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.pinknews.co.uk/2021/09/14/savage-x-fenty-fashion-show-rihanna-prime-video/|title=Gottmik and Troye Sivan among the truly incredible LGBT+ stars in Rihanna's new Savage x Fenty show|last=Yates|first=Johnny|work=PinkNews|access-date=September 19, 2021|date=September 14, 2021}}</ref> the "Crossover Latin King",<ref>{{cite news| url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-latin/sebastian-yatra-ricky-martin-falta-amor-2020-tour-973951|title=Sebastián Yatra, Ricky Martin Give 'Falta Amor' a Soulful Revamp|last=Exposito|first=Suzy|magazine=Rolling Stone|access-date=May 30, 2021|date=March 26, 2020}}</ref> the "Puerto Rican Pop King",<ref>{{cite news| url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/music/what-to-listen-to/pop-groups-solo-careers--gallery/ricky-martin--menudo-puerto-rican-pop-king-ricky-martin-short-fo |archive-url=https://ghostarchive.org/archive/20220111/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/music/what-to-listen-to/pop-groups-solo-careers--gallery/ricky-martin--menudo-puerto-rican-pop-king-ricky-martin-short-fo |archive-date=January 11, 2022 |url-access=subscription |url-status=live | title=From George Harrison to Zayn Malik: the pop stars who left their bands | access-date=March 28, 2019 |date=January 28, 2016 | work=[[The Daily Telegraph]]}}</ref> the "Salsa-Pop King",<ref>{{cite news|title=Concert vets offer nostalgia: Madonna drops new songs|url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/85650904/southtown-star/|newspaper=[[Daily Southtown|SouthtownStar]]|date=June 10, 1999|page=64|via=Newspapers.com|access-date=September 20, 2021}}</ref> and the "King of World Cup".<ref>{{cite news|url=https://rojakdaily.com/entertainment/article/5237/5-most-memorable-world-cup-anthems-of-all-time|title=5 Most Memorable World Cup Anthems Of All-Time|last=Chua|first=Jessica|work=Rojak Daily|access-date=April 8, 2021|date=June 22, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://us.hola.com/celebrities/gallery/20210802g0eq1ez4w3/honorific-nicknames-celebrities-are-known-for-in-popular-music/54|title=From 'King of Bachata' to 'Queen of Pop': List of honorific nicknames celebrities are known for in popular music|last=Gomez|first=Shirley|work=¡Hola!|access-date=August 15, 2021|date=August 2, 2021|archive-date=August 15, 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210815211921/https://us.hola.com/celebrities/gallery/20210802g0eq1ez4w3/honorific-nicknames-celebrities-are-known-for-in-popular-music/54|url-status=dead}}</ref> Martin is known as one of the most influential artists in the world.<ref name="E! influential"/> ''Billboard'' ranked him as one of the 30 Most Influential Latin Artists of All Time,<ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://www.billboard.com/photos/most-influential-latin-artists/1-most-influential-latin-acts-of-the-modern-era/|title=The 30 Most Influential Latin Artists of All Time|magazine=Billboard|date=April 28, 2015|access-date=January 31, 2022}}</ref> while NBC News introduced him as an "influential Latin celebrity".<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/news/latino/latino-celebrities-sign-open-letter-congress-gun-violence-n597731|title=Latino Celebrities Sign Open Letter to Congress on Gun Violence|publisher=NBC News|last=Wajda|first=Darek Michael|date=June 24, 2016|access-date=January 31, 2022}}</ref> In 2014, he won the award for the most influential international artist at the 18th [[China Music Awards]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/music-news/ricky-martin-david-beckham-coco-699490/|title=Ricky Martin, David Beckham, CoCo Lee Shine at China Music Awards|work=The Hollywood Reporter|last=Coonan|first=Clifford|date=April 28, 2014|access-date=January 31, 2022}}</ref> He was ranked among "25 musicians who broke barriers" by Stacker in 2019,<ref>{{cite news|url=https://stacker.com/stories/2864/25-musicians-who-broke-barriers|title=25 musicians who broke barriers|publisher=Stacker|last=Wiginton|first=Keri|date=April 18, 2019|access-date=January 31, 2022}}</ref> while in 2020, ''[[Spin (magazine)|Spin]]'' ranked him at number 27 on the list of "most influential artists of the past 35 years", as the only Latin artist on their list.<ref name="Spin">{{cite news| url=https://www.spin.com/2020/11/the-most-influential-artists-27-ricky-martin| title=The Most Influential Artists: #27 Ricky Martin|last=Villa|first=Lucas|work=[[Spin (magazine)|Spin]]| access-date=November 11, 2020 |date=November 10, 2020}}</ref> In 2022, Show News named him "the most influential global artist in history".<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.show.news/music/Ricky-Martin-Otra-noche-en-LA-suena-fuerte-desde-el-mar-20220201-0026.html|title=Ricky Martin, Otra noche en LA suena fuerte desde el mar|publisher=Show News|last=Rodríguez|first=Sayra|language=es|date=February 1, 2022|access-date=February 2, 2022}}</ref>

Martin's song "María (Pablo Flores Remix)", which was ranked among the "Greatest Latin Pop Song of All Time" by ''Rolling Stone'', and "11 remixes of classic Latin hits" by ''Billboard'', "launched the Latin and dance music crossover of the '90s", according to the latter.<ref name="RS Maria"/><ref name="Billboard remixes">{{cite magazine|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/latin/hispanic-heritage-2020-11-iconic-remixes-9449580/|title=Hispanic Heritage 2020: The Beat Goes On With 11 Iconic Remixes|last=Villa|first=Lucas|magazine=Billboard|access-date=August 22, 2021|date=September 16, 2020}}</ref> Olivier Pérou from ''[[Le Point]]'' commented that "some have even learned, thanks to him, to count to three in Spanish" following the popularity of the song.<ref name="Le Point"/> "La Copa de la Vida", which has been hailed as the Best World Cup Anthem of All-Time by multiple sources,<ref>Citations regarding "La Copa de la Vida" / "The Cup of Life" as the Best World Cup Anthem of All-Time:
* {{cite news|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2010/06/world-cup-songs-the-good-the-bad-the-bizarre/57651/|title=World Cup Songs: The Good, the Bad, the Bizarre|last=Barkhorn|first=Elenador|work=[[The Atlantic]]|access-date=April 5, 2021|date=June 4, 2010}}
* {{cite news|url=https://www.dallasobserver.com/music/the-10-best-world-cup-songs-of-all-time-7056329|title=The 10 Best World Cup Songs of All-Time|last=Tiscareno|first=Carmina|work=Dallas Observer|access-date=April 8, 2021|date=June 13, 2014}}
* {{cite news|url=https://www.thefader.com/2018/06/14/world-cup-anthems-songs-ricky-martin-shakira|title=Ranking the best World Cup anthems of all time|last=Paez-Pumar|first=Luis|work=[[The Fader]]|access-date=April 5, 2021|date=June 14, 2018}}
* {{cite news|url=https://en.prothomalo.com/entertainment/World-Cup-songs-that-shook-the-world|title=World Cup songs that shook the world|last=Nowrin|first=Nusrat|work=[[Prothom Alo]]|access-date=April 5, 2021|date=March 29, 2019}}
* {{cite news|url=https://onefootball.com/en/news/world-cup-countdown-ranking-the-best-ever-world-cup-songs-19673853|title=World Cup countdown: Ranking the best ever World Cup songs|last=Ambrose|first=Lewis|publisher=[[OneFootball]]|access-date=April 8, 2021|date=April 13, 2018}}
* {{cite news|url=https://theovertake.com/~beta/long-live-ricky-martin/|title=The Ultimate World Cup Song Powerlist|last=Sledge|first=Ben|publisher=[[The Overtake]]|access-date=April 8, 2021|date=April 13, 2018}}
* {{cite news|url=https://www.redbull.com/ar-es/temazos-futbol|title=Las 5 mejores canciones de los Mundiales|publisher=[[Red Bull]]|access-date=April 9, 2021|date=June 5, 2018|language=es}}
* {{cite news|url=https://remezcla.com/lists/music/best-world-cup-songs/|title=Latino Artists Have Gifted Us Some of the Best World Cup Songs|last=Hassan|first=Marcos|publisher=Remezcla|access-date=April 8, 2021|date=June 15, 2018|archive-date=May 14, 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210514234139/https://remezcla.com/lists/music/best-world-cup-songs/|url-status=dead}}
* {{cite news|url=https://rojakdaily.com/entertainment/article/5237/5-most-memorable-world-cup-anthems-of-all-time|title=5 Most Memorable World Cup Anthems Of All-Time|last=Chua|first=Jessica|work=Rojak Daily|access-date=April 8, 2021|date=June 22, 2018}}
* {{cite news| url=https://www.sportskeeda.com/football/4-of-the-best-world-cup-songs/3| title=4 of the best World Cup songs| publisher=Sportskeeda| access-date=April 5, 2021| date=September 13, 2020}}
* {{cite news|url=https://www.besoccer.com/new/7-most-sensational-fifa-world-cup-anthems-and-songs-of-all-time-916998|title=7 Most Sensational FIFA World Cup Anthems And Songs of All Time|publisher=BeSoccer|access-date=April 8, 2021|date=November 18, 2020}}
* {{cite news|url=https://www.buzzfeed.com/jessicalima/the-top-10-world-cup-songs|title=The Top 10 World Cup Songs Of All Time|last=Lima |first=Jessica|publisher=[[BuzzFeed]]|access-date=April 8, 2021|date=April 29, 2014}}</ref> became a "musical template" for World Cup anthems, and Martin's Latin and dance crossover style has been much copied in the anthems, as well as soccer chant "Ole! Ole! Ole!" in the lyrics, according to ''The Hollywood Reporter''.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/10-best-worst-wierdest-world-cup-songs-will-smith-waka-waka-1119305|title=The 10 Best, Worst and Weirdest World Cup Songs, From Will Smith to 'Waka Waka'|last=Roxborough|first=Scott|work=The Hollywood Reporter|access-date=April 8, 2021|date=June 12, 2018}}</ref> As believed by ''[[Esquire (magazine)|Esquire]]'', the song "inaugurated this musical subgenre" of Latin.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.esquire.com/es/actualidad/musica/a20511514/canciones-mundial-rusia-maluma-derulo-colors-shakira-ricky-martin/|title=Ranking de las mejores canciones del Mundial|last1=Cordero|first1=Gonzalo|last2=Gómez|first2=Celia|language=es|work=[[Esquire (magazine)|Esquire]]|access-date=April 9, 2021|date=September 5, 2018}}</ref> In his review for ''[[Pitchfork (website)|Pitchfork]]'', Corban Goble wrote that if World Cup anthems someday would be "given their own textbook", "La Copa de la Vida" would be "the standard-bearer for the whole genre".<ref name="Pitchfork">{{cite news|url=https://pitchfork.com/thepitch/355-fever-pitch-the-most-memorable-songs-of-the-world-cup/|title=Fever Pitch: The Most Memorable Songs of the World Cup|work=Pitchfork|access-date=April 8, 2021|date=June 3, 2014}}</ref>

